│   │   ├── AIScanner.jsx         ← Free AI analysis engine
│   │   ├── ProjectDropzone.jsx   ← Folder picker/dropper
│   │   ├── ProjectInfo.jsx       ← Project type badge
│   │   ├── Terminal.jsx          ← Streaming terminal
